Food Expert by Selectivor does not provide medical advice and is not a substitute for consultation and advice provided by a qualified and licensed health professional. title: Guess the name : Musical Instruments Quiz
details: Hey there, are you looking for a game which is fun to play and also educates you in learning new things in the process. Well, you have come to the right place. Our skill aims to help people recognize and differentiate between the sounds of different musical instruments using a fun quiz.  How to play:1. You will be asked a question followed by an instrument sound. Each question will have multiple choice answers. 2. Guess the instrument by listening to the sound. To give your answer, either repeat the number(one, two, three etc.) of the option or repeat the option value (drums, guitar, harmonica etc.) 3. After each set of questions, you will be given a score and the game will end.4. You can play again, to get a new set of sounds.NOTE: At any point in the game, say, START OVER, to restart the game or REPEAT, to repeat the question.

title: Story Starter by selfStarter VOICE EDUCATION
details: Help your child become a self starter! Just teach them to say, "Alexa, open Story Starter" then say "Student," and Alexa will give them a daily writing prompt. Educational exercises initiated by students can help them become independent learners, while at the same time, developing confidence in their ability to finish assignments.  After your child writes their response to the writing prompt, have them give it to you, and at your own leisure say, "Alexa, open Story Starter." title: Podcast Junkies
details: The pre-eminent (nice word, huh?) podcast for aficionados, connoisseurs, fans, proponents, and yes, junkies of all things podcast. Broadcast 3.0!

title: Podcast Junkies
example.1: “Alexa, tell Podcast Junkies to play the newest episode”
example.2: “Alexa, tell Podcast Junkies to go back 5 episodes”
example.3: “Alexa, tell Podcast Junkies to fast forward 2 minutes”
details: Podcast Junkies was born out of a genuine interest in and curiosity for this growing league of podcast hosts. It's hosted by Harry Duran. It features wide-ranging, authentic and sometimes candid interviews with this family of voices behind the microphone. The shows themselves cover a variety of topics such as Business, Finance Entrepreneurism, History, Comedy, Storytelling and more. Podcast Junkies explores the motivations behind the podcast's inception and allows the listener to connect on a more personal level with some of their favorite hosts.Here are a few quick tips when navigating our skill. First thing to note, when opening the skill you’ll be offered the latest episode, but if that’s not what you’re looking for, you can always find something more specific. This skill allows you to skip forward and backward by entire episodes, and you can also fast forward and rewind within episodes themselves. In addition, you can ask the skill to play the newest or oldest episodes released; or if you want to get specific, play a specific episode by saying the episode number. Try some of these commands:**Skip Entire Episodes**— [While Episode Is Playing] = “Alexa skip” or “Alexa tell Podcast Junkies to skip ahead 5 episodes”**Fast Forward/Back Within Episode**— [While Episode Is Playing] = “Alexa, tell Podcast Junkies to fast forward 2 minutes”— [While Episode Is Playing] = “Alexa, tell Podcast Junkies to rewind 45 seconds”**Select Newest Episode**— “Alexa, tell Podcast Junkies to play the newest episode”
